skdetail:

Invocation Name: villager quiz
des:
Play an New Horizons villager quiz with Alexa. Test your knowledge of villagers with Alexa and maybe learn some interesting trivia too!
To open the quiz say 'Alexa, start Villager quiz', while playing the quiz, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next question. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the quiz.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
